com.cyc.baseclient

Class CycObjectLibraryLoader

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cyc.baseclient.CycObjectLibraryLoader
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    KbObjectLibraryLoader

    public class CycObjectLibraryLoader
extends Object
    This class locates and loads classes cycFieldotated as CycObjectLibrary, and provides methods to access their fields. This is useful for verifying that a Cyc server's KB meets your code's requirements.
    Author:
    nwinant

      Nested Classes

      class  CycObjectLibraryLoader.CycLibraryField

      static interface  CycObjectLibraryLoader.CycLibraryFieldHandler
      Interface for an object which handles the results of a CycObjectLibraryLoader#processAllFieldsForClass
